== Overview ==
The Mechanical Obviator boosts hydro-servo performance by an amazing degree. The result is increased mobility and hull damage prevention.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Mechanical Obviator can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
